normal.question: If you have me, you want to share me. If you share me, you don't have me. What am I?
I have 2 hands, but 2 fingers. My number is 11 but others call me with 9. I walk along with 8 members. So can you tell me what am I?
We're five little items of an everyday sort, you'll find us all in "a tennis court".
We have 4 of us. But when you call us all, with the color of 2. Now we're in your area and hit you with that ddu du.
